{"tid":1590202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【928 雨革5周年】創新抗爭推上國際","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T16:31:55.000Z","uid":263563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cba9d4521ba88c4ae933da3678b8843c89b657","tid":1590202,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"其實國際媒體要放我地上頭版唔係咁易<br />\n恆常嘅警暴已經變左舊文 唔juicy <br />\n成日講和勇一體 <br />\n勇武真係做到加零一<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">火魔</span>愈黎愈成熟 <span style=\"color: orange;\">鶳</span>更係令班獅子狗少左個體行動<br />\n但和理非一方喺唱歌後 暫時未有新一輪攻勢<br />\n實在應該繼續集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n喺今日狗吠會yellow object後<br />\n有藝術家整左張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8vCDrn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8vCDrn.png&h=6c334921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟有個諗法<br />\n當年外國人好中意我地雨革成條金鐘馬路都係遮<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">適逢5周年，一於用最代表到雨革嘅黃色上街<br />\n每人cosplay一個公仔角色 最好小熊維尼<br />\n爭取gimmick 無嘅就黃色雨褸</span><br />\n無興趣嘅着番黑色black bloc勇武<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人認為28號集會咁夜 唔勇亦可<br />\n不如留力10月1日賀爆佢老母</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88HmkFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88HmkFS.jpg&h=6242bb06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qj6inUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQj6inUd.jpg&h=a8d187a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yRinUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yRinUe.jpg&h=64696a3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44a027c196cf2cb4676297d2cafd6158facf2f96","tid":1590202,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"171cb5271fe3ec38447453f4637c2c1174e2c86e","tid":1590202,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e628cb1a21b41ef587e865d8310a63d77a100bad","tid":1590202,"uid":53612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"全部人 著 黃雨褸<br />\n<br />\n= yellow object"},{"pid":"3f6532b695a3438b4fd893216cccc1a85090a12e","tid":1590202,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"另外亦想借位提下大家<br />\n見到<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>唔好掛住睇一擁而上<br />\n用得火，班狗好快推<br />\n你上前食花生 只會塞住魔法師走<br />\n比人捉哂 就無狗肉食<br />\n<br />\n見到<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>就企鬆啲<br />\n想影相打卡就番屋企啦<br />\n你點影都唔夠立場班記者影得靚"},{"pid":"cb7469a6527fe564f1374d0b018203953182b8f3","tid":1590202,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e628cb1a21b41ef587e865d8310a63d77a100bad","tid":1590202,"uid":53612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"全部人 著 黃雨褸<br />\n<br />\n= yellow object"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"fc5f311c783d5c4170ba9b743fdbfe22e9dc4b39","tid":1590202,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f6532b695a3438b4fd893216cccc1a85090a12e","tid":1590202,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"另外亦想借位提下大家<br />\n見到<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>唔好掛住睇一擁而上<br />\n用得火，班狗好快推<br />\n你上前食花生 只會塞住魔法師走<br />\n比人捉哂 就無狗肉食<br />\n<br />\n見到<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>就企鬆啲<br />\n想影相打卡就番屋企啦<br />\n你點影都唔夠立場班記者影得靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"火好危險架<br />\n細膽嘅見到好走啦"},{"pid":"5364aa22793ccd4e5da2ffdb607b0571ff2aa8e1","tid":1590202,"uid"